snippet.title: Donkey Kong Country 2: Diddy's Kong Quest Video Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This is a video walkthrough / playthrough / runthrough / etc of the SNES game Donkey Kong Country 2.

This game was the one I played the most out of the three SNES DKC games.  I spent ages on this game searching everywhere for all the bonus stages and so forth.  I recall how excited I was when I was finally able to get to the hidden end boss fight.  Intense stuff... :P

While I do collect the KONG letters here and there, for the most part I don't really try to bother with them since in the long run they don't do much for ya besides just giving you an extra life.
